<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contacto por Email - Zypher</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="contact-email.css">
</head>
<body>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #1e1e2e 0%, #16283d 100%);
            color: #ecf0f1;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .contact-container {
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0px 15px 30px rgba(22, 4, 51, 0.5);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #3498db;
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        p {
            color: #bdc3c7;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-top: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .email-link {
            color: #3498db;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .email-link:hover {
            color: #1abc9c;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>

    <div class="contact-container">
        <h1>Contacto por Email</h1>
        <p>Si prefieres el correo electrónico, puedes escribirnos a la siguiente dirección:</p>
        <a href="mailto:soporte@zypher.com" class="email-link">soporte@zypher.com</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
